rComments: Yes he is a traditional style teacher and can be annoyed if you're late but I don't blame him -- it's a turn off for a teacher and students when ppl come in late. But he is *insanely* knowledgeable, his lectures are interesting. He doesn't give A's unless you seriously prove that you are 100% into his course and submit excellent papers.

Professor Obeid is a kind and helpful person.  He genuinely wants students to do well and take an interest in the subject matter. The problem is many students take the class because they think it will be easy and they don't try.  I'm glad that the prof calls them out for talking and wasting everybody's time.  Try, show up and you will do well.
Dr. Obeid is a very knowledgable prof. His way of presenting his material is very deep and requires educated studentts to assimilates his way.
